Class Relation

  • java.lang.Object
    • tech.tablesaw.table.Relation
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Table, TemporaryView

    public abstract class Relation
extends Object
    A tabular data structure like a table in a relational database, but not formally implementing the relational algebra
